snippet.title: Sense of Darkness Gameplay Trailer v0.5
snippet.description:
Discover "Sense of Darkness," a unique VR game where you illuminate your path through touch. Dive into a world of hidden mysteries brought to life with light points. Coming soon on Steam. 

Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2822600/

Don't forget to subscribe for more updates.
